Servo 2	D6
Servo 3	D5
Servo 4	D10
Servo 5	D9
Servo 6	D11
RGB LED (Red)	D2
RGB LED (Green)	D4
RGB LED (Blue)	D7
Sensor 1 A0
Sensor 2 A1
Sensor 3 A2
Sensor 4 A3
